## Debugging Cheat Sheet
# If you see [missing servers] → check new additions in recent PRs
# If links are broken | GREP: grep "http.*404" curl validation
# If translation sync fails | GREP: grep "outdated.*README" git status
# If category is wrong → check alphabetical order per CONTRIBUTING.md guidelines
# If tests fail → run MCP Inspector at glama.ai/mcp/inspector for validation